plptool.mods

Class MemModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • plptool.PLPSimBusModule
        • plptool.mods.MemModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class MemModule
extends PLPSimBusModule
    PLP memory module. This module implements a wrapper read function that typecasts stored objects to Long.
